  m_Name: Demeter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  EventText: "A woman sits amid a field of flowers, her attention on a pair of figures
    sitting not far off. \r\n\u201CPlucked, buried, sown, risen,\r\nCycling sun and
    moonless skies.\r\nUnbroken sight, one love imprisoned,\r\nThe jailer gains unclouded
    eyes\u201D\r\nShe turns towards you, eyes shaded.\r\nShe reminds you most of\u2026\r"
